  <brief_title>Physiologic Effect of Topical Nitroglycerin on Microcirculation Capacity in Patients With Circulatory Shock: a Phase 0 Trial.</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 0 Trial of Topical Nitroglycerin on Microcirculation Capacity in Patients With Circulatory Shock.</official_title>
