  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This trial is an open-label, single center, Phase 0 trial that will enroll up to 25&#xD;
      participants with circulatory shock after cardiac surgery. Participants will be administered&#xD;
      a topical sublingual nitroglycerin solution and assessed for changes microcirculatory blood&#xD;
      flow using incident dark field microscopy.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
